install rar in centos5

1.download the latest version of rar for linux.
2.#tar -xvf rarlinux-3.9.3.tar.gz
3.enter rar directory #cd rar
4.install rar #make
5.if there is error like this:
"rar: /lib/libc.so.6: version `GLIBC_2.7' not found (required by rar)"
and then do this
#cp rar_static /usr/local/bin/rar
6.install done.
